title: Converse Rubber Tracks: Ready, Set - Earthquake Party! performs "Little Pet" + "Hello Weirdo"
description: Allston, Massachusetts up-and-comers, Earthquake Party! played their first POP Montréal this year, and swung by our studio to record a Ready, Set. The three-piece packed a punch of noise while tearing through an awesome combo of "Little Pet" + "Hello Weirdo."
